offees and all our Costa Ricans. For most of our coffees we work closely with importers who share the same guiding principals as ourselves and who pay a premium to secure high quality coffees. These importers work directly in producing countries sourcing coffees often purchasing from the same producers year after year which means we can continue to access amazing coffees.</p>'),(620,180,'_application','listify@mailinator.com'),(621,180,'_job_hours','a:7:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"start\";s:6:\"Closed\";s:3:\"end\";s:6:\"Closed\";}i:1;a:2:{s:5:\"start\";s:6:\"8:00am\";s:3:\"end\";s:6:\"5:00pm\";}i:2;a:2:{s:5:\"start\";s:6:\"8:00am\";s:3:\"end\";s:6:\"5:00pm\";}i:3;a:2:{s:5:\"start\";s:6:\"8:00am\";s:3:\"end\";s:6:\"5:00pm\";}i:4;a:2:{s:5:\"start\";s:6:\"8:00am\";s:3:\"end\";s:6:\"5:00pm\";}i:5;a:2:{s:5:\"start\";s:6:\"8:00am\";s:3:\"end\";s:6:\"5:00pm\";}i:6;a:2:{s:5:\"start\";s:6:\"8:00am\";s:3:\"end\";s:6:\"5:00pm\";}}'),(622,180,'_featured_image','http://acb61edc4a2275563075-7bb4b11e459e9adac234ac81abb4c5f3.r27.cf1.rackcdn.com/IMG_0027_retouched.jpg'),(623,180,'_gallery_images',''),(624,180,'_company_website','http://detourcoffee.com/cafe'),(625,180,'_company_video','https://vimeo.com/29229219'),(626,180,'_phone','(289) 238-8360'),(627,180,'_gallery','[gallery ids=&quot;&quot;]'),(628,180,'geolocation_lat','43.2662921'),(629,180,'geolocation_long','-79.9554838'),(630,180,'geolocation_formatted_address','41 King Street West, Dundas, ON L9H 1T5, Canada'),(631,180,'geolocation_street','41 King Street West'),(632,180,'geolocation_city','Hamilton'),(633,180,'geolocation_state_short','ON'),(634,180,'geolocation_state_long','Ontario'),(635,180,'geolocation_country_short','CA'),(636,180,'geolocation_country_long','Canada'),(637,180,'geolocation_postcode','L9H 1T5'),(638,180,'geolocated','1'),(639,180,'_job_expires','2014-12-01'),(640,180,'_products','a:2:{i:0;s:3:\"215\";i:1;s:3:\"203\";}'),(641,180,'rating','0'),(642,180,'_thumbnail_id','811'),(643,233,'_filled','0'),(644,233,'_fea