rs differ with respect to where they work, which services they are licensed to provide, and what name they use to refer to themselves. Part of this terminology difference depends on the regulations in a given location. Different states in the US vary on their labor and licensing laws. For example, in Maryland, a cosmetologist cannot use a straight razor, strictly reserved for barbers. In contrast, in New Jersey both are regulated by the State Board of Cosmetology and there is no longer a legal difference in barbers and cosmetologists, as they are issued the same license and can practice both the art of straight razor shaving, colouring, other chemical work and haircutting if they choose. In Australia, the official term for a barber is hairdresser; barber is only a popular title for men\'s hairdressers, although not as popular now as it was in the middle of the 20th century. Most would work in a hairdressing salon.</p>'),(870,685,'_application','contact@astoundify.com'),(871,685,'_job_hours','a:7:{i:1;a:2:{s:5:\"start\";s:7:\"9:00 am\";s:3:\"end\";s:7:\"5:00 pm\";}i:2;a:2:{s:5:\"start\";s:7:\"9:00 am\";s:3:\"end\";s:7:\"5:00 pm\";}i:3;a:2:{s:5:\"start\";s:7:\"9:00 am\";s:3:\"end\";s:7:\"5:00 pm\";}i:4;a:2:{s:5:\"start\";s:7:\"9:00 am\";s:3:\"end\";s:7:\"5:00 pm\";}i:5;a:2:{s:5:\"start\";s:7:\"9:00 am\";s:3:\"end\";s:7:\"5:00 pm\";}i:6;a:2:{s:5:\"start\";s:7:\"9:00 am\";s:3:\"end\";s:7:\"7:00 pm\";}i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"start\";s:6:\"Closed\";s:3:\"end\";s:6:\"Closed\";}}'),(872,685,'_featured_image','http://acb61edc4a2275563075-7bb4b11e459e9adac234ac81abb4c5f3.r27.cf1.rackcdn.com/IMG_9840.jpg'),(873,685,'_gallery_images','a:3:{i:0;s:97:\"http://local.shadighar.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/81578af994b-a0f6-4186-8f42-fa52c0caf27d.jpg\";i:1;s:82:\"http://local.shadighar.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/15757079382_a61f5c8e62_o.jpg\";i:2;s:88:\"http://local.shadighar.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/foodiesfeed.com_mobile-coffee8.jpg\";}'),(874,685,'_company_website','https://ast